name: Dr. Sarah Thompson
title: Senior Career Coach
bio: Dr. Sarah Thompson has over 15 years of experience in career counseling, helping professionals transition smoothly to new career paths and develop strong personal brands.

name: Johnathan Lee
title: Resume Expert & Interview Coach
bio: Johnathan is dedicated to helping job seekers create impactful resumes and ace their interviews. With a background in HR, he brings valuable insights into what employers are looking for.

name: Emily Chen
title: LinkedIn Profile Optimization Specialist
bio: Emily is passionate about helping professionals make the most out of LinkedIn. Her strategies help clients stand out and build valuable connections in their industry.

name: Michael Carter
title: Career Development Mentor
bio: Michael has been guiding young professionals and students to make informed career decisions. His expertise in skill development helps clients achieve long-term career goals.

name: Sophia Martinez
title: Salary Negotiation Coach
bio: Sophia specializes in helping professionals negotiate salaries and benefits, ensuring they achieve the compensation they deserve.

name: David Patel
title: Work-Life Balance Coach
bio: With a focus on balancing personal and professional life, David provides strategies for managing time and reducing stress for greater job satisfaction.
